item.title: Fred is graduating!
item.description: 20:52 Monday 28 November 2016 JST 95% of the replies are like, “sorry I can’t be there” but Fred’s having a party.. I mean I guess it’s a bit fuckin late to throw a big party 3 days ahead of time, but yeah I wish I could be there. Come on, teleportation!
